{"title":"总是母亲（三首）——写在发工资的日子","authors":["高凯"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":2,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是母亲（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在发工资的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高凯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取暖补贴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那双缝棉袄的手么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那双掖被子的手么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你记不记得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再寒冷的冬天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要母亲在家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上总是热的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书报费"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要好好念书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要好好念书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲几乎每天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要这样叮咛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油灯下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面容慈祥的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是要一次次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把揉皱的课本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻抚平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是她用卖鸡蛋的钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我买的课本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原补贴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在高处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲总是想扶着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再三提醒千万小心、小心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在高处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会感到母亲的爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比你站得更高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如高原的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照在心上"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}